<subSubSection pageId="243" pageNumber="848" type="conservation">
<paragraph blockId="243.[178,1383,248,476]" pageId="243" pageNumber="848">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[179,526,281,315]" pageId="243" pageNumber="848">Status and Conservation.</emphasis>
Classified as Endangered on The IUCN Red List. Van Deusen’s New Guinea Mountain Rat has a very restricted distribution, is relatively uncommon, and is probably threatened by habitat loss and degradation.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
